界面新闻是中国具有影响力的原创财经新媒体，只服务于独立思考的人群。
Interface News is an original and influential new financial media in China, serving only the people who think independently.
图片来源：法尔斯通讯社“ 部分民众乘学校关门之际，在波斯新年到来前赶往里海等其他度假胜地过新年。
Source: Fars News Agency. "Some people travel to other holiday resorts such as the Caspian Sea before the Persian New Year when schools close.
伊朗当局已警告，如有需要，可能动用“武力”限制各地间通行。
Iranian authorities have warned that "force" could be used to restrict movement between locations if necessary.
”伊朗卫生部3月7日下午宣布，过去24小时内，伊朗新型冠状病毒肺炎新增确诊病例1076例，累计确诊病例达5823例。
Iran's new coronavirus pneumonia has been confirmed in 1,076 new cases in the past 24 hours, bringing the total number of confirmed cases to 5,823, the Health Ministry said this afternoon.
其中，死亡病例新增21例，累计死亡病例升至145例。
Of these, there were 21 new deaths and the cumulative number of deaths rose to 145.
在所有确诊病例中，1669例已治愈。
Of the total number of confirmed cases, 1,669 have been cured.
据《伊朗头条》报道，伊朗卫生部发言人贾汉普尔（Kianoush Jahanpour）指出，目前全国有1.6万疑似病例正在医院接受观察检测。
Iranian Health Ministry spokesman Kianoush Jahanpour says 16,000 suspected cases are being tested in hospitals across the country, according to Iran's headlines.
在确诊病例中，首都德黑兰确诊人数最多，达1539人；其次为圣城库姆668例；北部马赞德兰省606例。
Of the confirmed cases, Tehran, the capital, recorded the highest number of confirmed cases, 1,539, followed by the holy city of Qom 668 and the northern province of Mazandran with 606 cases.
周六上午，新当选的议员拉赫巴尔（Fatema Rahbar）在德黑兰去世，成为伊朗首位因感染新冠肺炎去世的女性政客。
On Saturday morning, Fatema Rahbar, the newly elected member of parliament, died in Tehran, becoming Iran's first female politician to die of pneumonia.
拉赫巴尔出生于1964年，是保守派伊斯兰联合党成员。
Born in 1964, Rahbar was a member of the conservative United Islamic Party.
她于2004年到2016年担任议会议员，后又在今年2月21日的议会选举中再度当选。
She served as a member of Parliament from 2004 to 2016 and was re-elected in the parliamentary elections of 21 February this year.
截至目前，伊朗已有23名议员确诊感染，占总议员人数的8%。
So far, 23 members of parliament have been diagnosed with infection, accounting for 8 per cent of the total.
周四，伊朗驻叙利亚前大使、外长扎里夫的前顾问谢赫伊斯兰（Hossein Sheikholeslam）也因感染新冠肺炎去世。
On Thursday, Hossein Sheikholeslam, Iran's former ambassador to Syria and former adviser to Foreign Minister Nawaz Zarif, also died of pneumonia.
谢赫伊斯兰曾参与了1979年的德黑兰人质事件。
Sheikh Islam was involved in the 1979 Tehran hostage incident.
伊朗驻比利时大使馆周六发表声明称，伊朗欢迎国际社会就防控疫情提供的任何支持和意见。
In a statement Saturday, the Iranian embassy in Belgium said Iran welcomes any support and advice from the international community on the prevention and control of the outbreak.
声明指出，目前伊朗的周五礼拜、文化和体育活动都已暂停，全国所有学校关闭，直至波斯新年开始。
The statement noted that Friday worship, cultural and sports activities in Iran had been suspended and that all schools were closed until the beginning of the Persian New Year.
波斯新年为每年的3月21日。
The Persian New Year is on March 21 of each year.
《卫报》援引伊朗当地媒体报道称，部分民众乘学校关门之际，在波斯新年到来前赶往里海等其他度假胜地过新年。
The Guardian quoted local Iranian media as saying some people were rushing to other holiday resorts, such as the Caspian Sea, before the Persian New Year when the school closed.
有消息称，周五晚上，由于民众驾车出城，德黑兰部分地区甚至出现了堵车。
There were reports of traffic jams in parts of Tehran on Friday night as people drove out of the city.
在里海附近的度假热门地马赞达兰省和吉兰省，伊斯兰革命卫队已经设立检查站，对过往车辆进行检查。
In the popular Caspian Sea resort provinces of Mazandaran and Gilan, the Islamic Revolutionary Guard Corps has set up checkpoints to inspect passing vehicles.
伊朗当局此前警告，如果有需要，可能动用“武力”限制各地之间的通行。
Iranian authorities have previously warned that "force" could be used to restrict movement between locations if needed.
伊朗传染病专家、伊朗国家流感委员会委员马尔达尼（Masoud Mardani）本周预测，未来两周，德黑兰可能有多达40%的人感染新冠病毒。
Masoud Mardani, an Iranian infectious disease specialist and member of Iran's National Influenza Committee, this week predicted that as many as 40% of Tehran's population could become infected with the new crown virus over the next two weeks.
世界卫生组织伊朗办公室负责人哈姆勒曼（Christoph Hamelmann）在对其他国家外交官讲话时指出，伊朗目前急需资金升级实验室检测设备和临床治疗设施。
Speaking to diplomats in other countries, Christoph Hamelmann, head of the World Health Organization's Iran office, said Iran urgently needs funds to upgrade laboratory testing equipment and clinical treatment facilities.
阿联酋、科威特、巴林、沙特阿拉伯等国已经暂停往来伊朗的航班。
The United Arab Emirates, Kuwait, Bahrain, Saudi Arabia and other countries have suspended flights to and from Iran.
沙特呼吁在过去14天到过伊朗的沙特公民主动向当局报告。
Saudi Arabia calls on Saudi citizens who have visited Iran in the past 14 days to report to the authorities on their own initiative.
至此，中东地区的确诊病例已经超过6000例。
So far, more than 6,000 cases have been confirmed in the Middle East.
